# Normalize line endings on commit. Working tree CRLF on Windows is fine
# (left to Git's auto-conversion based on core.autocrlf), but the repository
# always stores LF — this prevents the whole-file-modified phantom diffs we
# saw on the first Windows roundtrip.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lock files: never touched manually; force LF everywhere.
package-lock.json text eol=lf

# Binary assets (none right now, but pin the rule in case art lands later).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
